quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  54,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  54,1,qayamat ki gharri qareeb aa gayi aur chaand phatt gaya
  54,2,magar inn logon ka haal yeh hai ke khuwa koi nishani dekh len mun mourr jatay hain aur kehte hain yeh to chalta howa jaadoo hai
  54,3,unhon ne ( is ko bhi ) jhutla diya aur apni khwahisaat nafs hi ki pairwi ki har maamla ko aakhir-kaar aik injaam par poanch kar rehna hai
  54,4,inn logon ke samnay ( pichli qomon ke ) woh halaat aa chuke hain jin mein sar kashi se baz rakhnay ke liye kaafi samaan Ibrat hai
  54,5,aur aisi hikmat jo nasiyaat ke maqsad ko badarja atam poora karti hai magar tnbihat inn par kargar nahi hoten
  54,6,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se rukh phair lau jis roz pukarnay wala aik sakht nagawaar cheez ki taraf pukare ga"
  54,7,log sehmi hui nigahon ke sath apni qabron se iss terhan nikleen ge goya woh bhikri hui tidyan hain
  54,8,pukarnay walay ki taraf doray ja rahay hon ge aur wohi munkareen ( jo duniya mein is ka inkaar karte thay ) uss waqt kahin ge ke yeh din to bara kathin hai
  54,9,"inn se pehlay Nooh ki qoum jhutla chuki hai onhon ne hamaray bande ko jhoota qarar diya aur kaha ke yeh deewana hai, aur woh buri terhanjihrkagaya"
  54,10,"aakhir-kaar uss ne apne rab ko puraka ke"" mein maghloob ho chuka, ab to inn se intiqam le """
  54,11,tab hum ne mosla dhaar barish se aasman ke darwazay khol diye aur zameen ko phaar kar chashmon mein tabdeel kar diya
  54,12,aur yeh sara pani uss kaam ko poora karne liye mil gaya jo muqaddar ho chuka tha
  54,13,aur Nooh ko hum ne aik takhton aur kilon wali par sawaar kar diya
  54,14,jo hamari nigrani mein chal rahi thi yeh tha badla uss shakhs ki khatir jis ki na qadri ki gayi thi
  54,15,"uss kashti ko hum ne aik nishani bana kar chore diya, phir koi hai nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
  54,16,"dekh lau, kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi theen meri tnbihat"
  54,17,"hum ne iss quran ko nasiyaat ke liye aasaan zareya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
  54,18,"Aad ne jhtlaya, to dekh lau ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi theen meri tnbihat"
  54,19,hum ne aik pihm nahosat ke din sakht tofani howa unn par bhaij di jo logon ko utha utha kar is terhan pheink rahi thi
  54,20,jaisay woh jarr se akhrhe hue khajoor ke tanay hon
  54,21,pas dekh lau ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi theen meri tnbihat
  54,22,"hum ne iss quran ko nasiyaat ke liye aasaan zareya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
  54,23,samood ne tnbihat ko jhtlaya
  54,24,"aur kehnay lagey"" aik akela aadmi jo hum hi mein se hai kya ab hum uss ke peechay chalein? iss ka itebaa hum qubool kar len to iss ke maienay yeh hon ge ke hum behak gay hain aur hamari aqal maari gayi hai"
  54,25,"kya hamaray darmain bas yahishakhs tha jis par khuda ka zikar nazil kya gaya? nahi, balkay yeh parlay darjay ka jhoota aur Bar khud ghalat hai """
  54,26,"( hum ne apne paighambar se kaha )"" kal hi aِnhin maloom howa jata hai ke kon parlay darjay ka jhoota aur Bar khud ghalat hai"
  54,27,hum oontni ko inn ke liye fitnah bana kar bhaij rahay hain ab zara sabr ke sath dekh ke inn ka kya injaam hota hai
  54,28,"inn ko jta day ke pani inn ke aur oontni ke darmain taqseem hoga aur har aik apni baari ke din pani par aeye ga """
  54,29,aakhir-kaar unn logon ne apne aadmi ko puraka aur uss ne iss kaam ka bera uthaya aur oontni ko maar dala
  54,30,phir dekh lau ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi theen meri tnbihat
  54,31,hum ne unn par bas aik hi dhamaka chorra aur woh baray walay ki rondi hui barh ki terhan bhus ho kar reh gay
  54,32,"hum ne iss quran ko nasiyaat ke liye aasaan zareya bana diya hai, ab hai koi nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
  54,33,loot ki qoum ne tnbihat ko jhtlaya
  54,34,aur hum ne pathrao karne wali howa is par bhaij di sirf loot ke ghar walay uss se mehfooz rahay
  54,35,unn ko hum ne apne fazl se raat ke pichlle pehar bacha kar nikaal diya yeh jaza dete hain hum har uss shakhs ko jo shukar guzaar hota hai
  54,36,loot ne apni qoum ke logon ko hamari pakar se khabardaar kya magar woh saari tnbihat ko mashkook samajh kar baton mein uratay rahay
  54,37,phir unhon ne ussay apne mehmanon ki hifazat se baz rakhnay ki koshish ki aakhir-kaar hum ne unn ki ankhen moond den ke chako ab mere azaab aur meri tnbihat ka maza
  54,38,subah saweray hi aik atal azaab ne un ko aa liya
  54,39,chako maza ab mere azaab ka aur meri tnbihat ka
  54,40,"hum ne iss quran ko nasiyaat ke liye aasaan zareya bana diya hai, pas hai koi nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
  54,41,aur all firaon ke paas bhi tnbihat aayi theen
  54,42,magar unhon ne hamari saari nshanyon ko jhutla diya aakhir ko hum ne inhen pakra jis terhan koi zabardast qudrat wala pokarta hai
  54,43,kya tumahray kufar kuch unn logon se behtar hain? ya aasmani kitabon mein tumahray liye koi maffi likhi hui hai ?
  54,44,"ya inn logon ka kehna yeh hai ke hum aik mazboot jatha hain, apna bachao kar len ge ?"
  54,45,anqareeb yeh jatha shikast kha jaye ga aur yeh sab peeth phair kar bhagtay nazar ayen ge
  54,46,balkay inn se nimatnay ke liye asal waday ka waqt to qayamat hai aur woh barri aafat aur ziyada talkh saa-at hai
  54,47,yeh mujrim log Dur haqeeqat ghalat fehmi mein mein mubtala hain aur inn ki aqal maari gayi hai
  54,48,jis roz yeh mun ke bil aag mein ghsite jayen ge uss roz inn se kaha jaye ga ke ab chako jahannum ki lapat ka maza
  54,49,hum ne har cheez aik taqdeer ke sath peda ki hai
  54,50,aur hamara hukum bas aik hi hukum hota hai aur palak jhupkatay woh amal mein aa jata hai
  54,51,"tum jaisay bohat soon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain, phir hai koi nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
  54,52,jo kuch unhon ne kya hai woh sab dftron mein darj hai
  54,53,aur har choti barri baat likhi hui mojood hai
  54,54,nafarmani se parhaiz karne walay yaqeenan baghoon aur nﮦron mein hon ge
  54,55,"sachhi izzat ki jagah, barray Zee Iqtidaar badshah ke qareeb"
